Interface Response<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The deserialized type of the response content, available from Response.getValue().
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PagedResponse<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FilesystemsCreateResponse, FilesystemsDeleteResponse, FilesystemsGetPropertiesResponse, FilesystemsListResponse, FilesystemsSetPropertiesResponse, PathsCreateResponse, PathsDeleteResponse, PathsGetPropertiesResponse, PathsLeaseResponse, PathsListResponse, PathsReadResponse, PathsUpdateResponse, ResponseBase, SimpleResponse, StreamResponse

    REST response with a strongly-typed content specified.
